 openssl
Suggests:
 certbot
Description: NAS Panel Web Server
 High-performance C++20 reverse proxy for NAS Panel.
 .
 Features:
  - HTTP/1.1 and HTTP/2 (nghttp2)
  - Reverse proxy with upstream pooling and health checks
  - TLS/SSL via OpenSSL 3 with ACME/Let's Encrypt (HTTP-01, DNS-01)
  - Lua 5.4 scripting middleware per location
  - LRU response cache with TTL and RFC 7234 Cache-Control
  - Token-bucket rate limiter per client IP
  - Static file serving: gzip, brotli, ETag, Range, SPA fallback
  - WebSocket proxying
  - Admin panel at /np_admin with Basic Auth, IP allowlist,
    real-time dashboard charts, audit log, SSE live log
  - Built-in health: /apis/healths /apis/heartbeat /apis/ping
